      <text>It is said that Lady Ferandal Vorgatine has returned home after a long
absence.  This arrival has sent rumors drifting through the air as to her
reasons, and the circumstances of several changes to her person.  The most
obvious reason for her return is the upcoming birthday of her mother, Lady
Claire Vorgatine, yet there is doubt as to that being the true reason for
her return with the absence of her siblings Serandal and Verandal.  Only
time will tell what her return truly means, and there is no doubt that it
will be revealed to open ears in due time.    
